&lt;div data-qa=&quot;block-kit-renderer&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;The Ingredients Club team is a lean, high-impact group responsible for building and scaling CookUnity’s group purchasing and restaurant partnership ecosystem. The team works closely with chefs, suppliers, and internal teams to deliver cost savings, operational efficiencies, and long term supply chain value in support of CookUnity’s mission to connect eaters with the world’s best chefs.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
