&lt;h3&gt;The role:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Customer Support Specialist is responsible for providing high-quality operational support across CookUnity’s two primary B2B verticals: &lt;strong&gt;Bulk Meal Programs for corporate clients and Smart Fridge workplace solutions&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role manages inbound tickets from both &lt;strong&gt;B2B client stakeholders and Smart Fridge end-users&lt;/strong&gt;, ensuring issues are resolved quickly while maintaining a reliable and professional experience.&lt;/p&gt;
