&lt;li&gt;Advise on Food is Medicine, Medically Tailored Meals, supplemental benefits (including Medicare Advantage SSBCI and SNP frameworks), Medicaid 1115 waivers, and similar healthcare-funded meal programs.&lt;/li&gt;
