&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Food has lost its soul to modern convenience. And with it, it has lost the power to nourish, inspire, and connect us. So in 2018, CookUnity was founded as the first-of-its-kind platform that connects the world with the source of truly great food: chefs. Today, CookUnity delivers 50 million meals a year from the industry’s best chefs to homes all over the country. Fresh. Ready-to-eat. And crafted with the passion that nourishes body and soul.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;Unwilling to stop there, CookUnity is expanding beyond delivery to become an ever-innovating marketplace focused on our singular mission: &lt;strong data-stringify-type=&quot;bold&quot;&gt;empower Chefs to nourish the world.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;If that mission has you hungry in more ways than one, you’ve found the right job posting.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Dishwasher will be responsible for maintaining a clean, sanitary, and organized kitchen environment by washing dishes, utensils, and kitchen equipment, ensuring that everything is ready for daily operations. This role is vital to keeping the kitchen running smoothly and contributing to our overall food safety and customer satisfaction standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Wash dishes, pots, pans, utensils, and glassware, ensuring that they are clean and sanitized in a timely manner.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain cleanliness of kitchen floors, walls, and other work areas, ensuring they are free from debris and food residue.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Operate and maintain dishwashing machines and other kitchen cleaning equipment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Sort and store clean dishes and utensils in the appropriate areas.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the removal of trash and recycling, ensuring the kitchen is kept clean and free of waste.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist kitchen staff with cleaning and maintaining kitchen equipment and supplies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow food safety and sanitation guidelines to ensure a safe and clean work environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restock cleaning supplies and ensure that all equipment is operational.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Qualifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to work in a fast-paced environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong attention to detail and ability to follow instructions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Basic knowledge of kitchen safety and sanitation practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to stand for long periods, lift up to 50 lbs, and work in a physically demanding environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive attitude, strong work ethic, and teamwork mentality.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🩺&amp;nbsp; Health Insurance coverage with Cigna&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;✅&amp;nbsp; Weekly payments&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🚀 Opportunity for advancement&lt;/p&gt;
